01:55:25.334 --> 01:55:29.198
A few days ago, they brought
some furniture to the villa opposite.

01:55:32.751 --> 01:55:33.913
Did you notice?

01:55:34.709 --> 01:55:37.577
I think so,
but I don't see much from in here.

01:55:38.293 --> 01:55:39.323
Ask her.

01:55:47.376 --> 01:55:48.785
Claire?

01:55:48.959 --> 01:55:51.413
Listen to what
this gentleman wants to say.

01:55:52.543 --> 01:55:53.573
(Claire) Yes.

01:55:54.959 --> 01:55:56.369
And the day after,

01:55:56.543 --> 01:55:59.790
other workmen came
and took everything away again.

01:56:01.918 --> 01:56:03.458
The day after?

01:56:04.751 --> 01:56:08.697
In 18 months,
three deliveries and three removals.

01:56:11.668 --> 01:56:13.954
I was here a while ago.

01:56:15.251 --> 01:56:17.455
- Do you remember?
- Nine.

01:56:19.918 --> 01:56:23.864
- What do you mean?
- You've been here nine times.

01:56:25.918 --> 01:56:27.375
Today makes 10.

01:56:27.709 --> 01:56:31.324
I was wondering if you saw
a woman leave the villa.

01:56:32.584 --> 01:56:35.784
Medium height, light hair,
a bit pale?

01:56:37.084 --> 01:56:40.948
- Yes.
- That time was 231.

01:56:42.543 --> 01:56:44.000
Are you sure?

01:56:44.334 --> 01:56:45.993
Then another six.

01:56:46.834 --> 01:56:51.788
In a year and a half,
I saw her go out 237 times.

01:56:52.168 --> 01:56:53.577
(barman) What did I say?

01:56:53.751 --> 01:56:56.204
She's a phenomenon,
remembers everything.

01:56:58.251 --> 01:56:59.792
It's not possible.

01:57:02.334 --> 01:57:04.455
You were at the villa 63 times.

01:57:04.793 --> 01:57:08.703
36 during the day and 27 at night,

01:57:09.043 --> 01:57:11.366
excluding the night
of the accident.

01:57:12.834 --> 01:57:16.247
- One, four, four.
- One, four, four?

01:57:16.584 --> 01:57:18.824
The telephone number
for the ambulance.

01:57:20.293 --> 01:57:21.869
The villa is free now.

01:57:22.251 --> 01:57:25.166
If you're interested,
I'll get you a good deal.

01:57:26.793 --> 01:57:29.411
- Who owns it?
- Me.

01:57:30.626 --> 01:57:32.700
But I don't know what to do with it.

01:57:33.793 --> 01:57:36.459
I often rent it out to cinema people.

01:57:37.376 --> 01:57:38.750
Cinema people?

01:57:39.334 --> 01:57:42.285
For the past two years,
it's been taken by the engineer

01:57:42.459 --> 01:57:44.995
who does the lift
that takes me up to my house.

01:57:45.793 --> 01:57:47.499
He's really nice, that boy.

01:57:48.418 --> 01:57:50.076
He can do anything.

01:57:50.251 --> 01:57:52.740
There's nothing he can't fix.

01:57:53.334 --> 01:57:56.665
And he's always kissing me.
(giggles)

01:57:56.834 --> 01:57:58.624
Bringing me flowers.

01:57:59.876 --> 01:58:02.116
(ethereal instrumental music)

01:58:47.834 --> 01:58:49.908
(ringing tone)

01:59:06.959 --> 01:59:08.500
(music intensifies)

