(Claire moans)

02:00:43.959 --> 02:00:47.740
(loudspeaker) The Paris Express
is now arriving at platform seven.

02:00:49.209 --> 02:00:50.916
Your attention, please.

02:00:51.084 --> 02:00:53.917
The Berlin-Prague Arrow
is running 40 minutes late

02:00:54.084 --> 02:00:55.281
