02:00:57.126 --> 02:00:58.667
Come in, sir.

02:01:00.001 --> 02:01:02.371
We furnished it
exactly as you requested.

02:01:03.793 --> 02:01:06.281
And tomorrow, your trunks
will be delivered.

02:01:06.459 --> 02:01:09.576
And later, I'll pass by
with a copy of your contract.

02:01:09.918 --> 02:01:13.283
If there's anything else,
please don't hesitate to call.

02:01:19.751 --> 02:01:21.292
Oh, Virgil.

02:01:22.709 --> 02:01:26.917
If anything should happen to us,
I want you to know that I do love you.

